\item \strong{Matrix Mode (Existing)}: \code{nmfkc(Y=matrix, A=matrix, ...)}
\item \strong{Formula Mode (New)}: \code{nmfkc(formula=Y_vars ~ A_vars, data=df, rank=Q, ...)}
